content: Note - You can actually warp back to the Zhu Estate in the previous area to find the village in a different light. From some reason it will be daylight when you return, and nearly all the enemies will be gone, save for a Lantern Holder that opened the door for you where you fought the Second Sister. Defeat this lone foe, and you'll be able to claim the Lantern Holder Spirit!
